rket Share<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/turbocharging-your-business-with-banking-services\/#3-focus-on-flexibility-to-inspire-innovation\" title=\"3. Focus on Flexibility to Inspire Innovation\">3. Focus on Flexibility to Inspire Innovation<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/turbocharging-your-business-with-banking-services\/#why-you-should-align-banking-services-and-your-business\" title=\"Why You Should Align Banking Services and Your Business\">Why You Should Align Banking Services and Your Business<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/turbocharging-your-business-with-banking-services\/#the-essentials-needed-to-align-business-goals-and-banking-services\" title=\"The Essentials Needed to Align Business Goals and Banking Services\">The Essentials Needed to Align Business Goals and Banking Services<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/turbocharging-your-business-with-banking-services\/#seeks-insights-from-all-the-company-executives\" title=\"Seeks Insights from All the Company Executives\">Seeks Insights from All the Company Executives<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/turbocharging-your-business-with-banking-services\/#prepare-a-long-term-vision-for-the-company\" title=\"Prepare a Long-term Vision for the Company\">Prepare a Long-term Vision for the Company<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"aligning-banking-services-and-your-business\"><\/span>Aligning Banking Services and Your Business<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>According to a <a href=\"http:\/\/www.pwc.com\/us\/en\/financial-services\/research-institute\/assets\/pwc-top-financial-services-issues-2017.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2017 financial service paper by PWC<\/a>, aligning your business goals and banking services requires you to shift your priorities to certain areas such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Trying to contain your business costs<\/li><li>Doing what you can to protect your existing market share from competitors<\/li><li>Looking for new revenue streams<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>So, how can balancing banking services and your business promote innovation, grow the owner&#8217;s bank account, and reduce corporate expenses? Read on to learn why you need to understand the company as a whole before executing any strategy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1-focus-on-efficiency-to-lower-your-corporate-expenses\"><\/span>1. Focus on Efficiency to Lower Your Corporate Expenses<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The first thing you have to do is <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/how-do-banks-innovate-and-grow-in-a-digital-age\/#:~:text=is%20how%20banks-,innovate,-and%20grow%20in\">innovate<\/a>. Innovating enables you to detect costly banking transactions and business processes. Use this information to develop new and more efficient ways of performing these processes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, if you find that the technical support labour costs have suddenly become high, you should ask yourself why this is the case. In such a scenario, you may find that the answer to this problem involves:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Developing a central repository to enable employees to locate the technical support resources much faster<\/li><li>Or provide an FAQ section on the website that addresses the time-consuming recurring questions.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also need to assess the type of learning happening in the organization. Balancing your business goals and banking services involves accepting that some learning instances can prove counterproductive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do away with any learning that the employees aren&#8217;t applying to their roles. Scrap learning allows the company to save money, time, and resources. It also ensures that you get to eliminate all instances of negative learning.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-improve-customer-service-on-the-banking-as-a-service-platform-to-protect-your-market-share\"><\/span>2. Improve Customer Service on the Banking as a Service Platform to Protect Your Market Share<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>In trying to align your banking services and your business goals, you&#8217;ll come to learn that happy customers are always loyal. When the customers are happy, this will translate to:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Referrals through word of mouth and social shares<\/li><li>Customer evangelism<\/li><li>Better customer retention rates<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s why you need to ensure that your personnel better understand client concerns, questions, and general needs. A better understanding of these three issues guarantees that they&#8217;re better equipped to engage the clients.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Moreover, employees with a good understanding of the company&#8217;s offerings will increase sales, translating to better returns. Remember that no one likes to wait in line, especially when using <a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/business-opportunies-with-banking-as-a-service-baas\/#:~:text=finance%20experts%20call-,Banking%20as%20a%20Service,-(Baas).\">banking as a service<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Streamlining online support through friendly and highly skilled support agents ensures that customers get their queries answered faster. It also reduces the amount of time spent waiting for a response from the support team.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What&#8217;s the Status of Your Mobile Application and Official Website?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aligning your business goals and banking services involves much more than reducing the customer wait times. It involves looking at the state of your mobile applications and official website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You need to ask yourself one simple question \u2013 are the applications and official website easy to use, well designed, and intuitive? If they are lacking, you should sit down with the tech team to ensure that they get a better understanding of customer needs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When improving the mobile application, for example, they should make several applications to the existing apps to ensure they include:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Touch ID login<\/li><li>Mobile check deposit<\/li><li>Notifications to inform clients of potential fraud alerts<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Customers will, in most cases, walk away if they can&#8217;t find the information they want on your website. The same applies when the banking as a service platform turns out to be too complicated.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/innovation-in-services.jpg\" alt=\"innovation in services\" class=\"wp-image-822\" srcset=\"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/innovation-in-services.jpg 800w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/innovation-in-services-300x150.jpg 300w, http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/innovation-in-services-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3-focus-on-flexibility-to-inspire-innovation\"><\/span>3. Focus on Flexibility to Inspire Innovation<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As a business leader, you should note that staying the same will cause you to fall behind. It&#8217;s a principle that applies to employee training and development programs. Balancing banking services and your business will require you to focus on expansion and ongoing innovation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>They are the factors that will ensure that the workforce remains adaptable and flexible. It calls for you to ensure that the employees have continued access to company resources. These resources should have their preferred formats to ensure that anyone can use them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Company personnel will become more inclined to align business goals and banking services when they have access to resources suited to their needs. The company, therefore, has no option but to provide a modern ecosystem that supports learning and tracks performance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"why-you-should-align-banking-services-and-your-business\"><\/span>Why You Should Align Banking Services and Your Business<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your company roadmap doesn&#8217;t have enough visibility, this may be the right time to start advocating for its inclusion. The same holds if your team doesn&#8217;t have a seat at the decision-making table.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Use these three reasons to show why aligning business goals and banking services should become a priority in the next budgeting season:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>The budgeting process will cease being administrative: Aligning your business goals with banking means, budgeting stops being a job you must complete and becomes an extension of its operations.<\/li><li>Resource allocation will become easier: Resources are never enough, regardless of the company&#8217;s size. Unhealthy allocation leads to bad practices. Alignment ensures resources get allocated based on where they are needed.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;III. It ensures you&#8217;ll have enough money if the need ever arises: Failure to align means available resources will become too thinly spread.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-essentials-needed-to-align-business-goals-and-banking-services\"><\/span>The Essentials Needed to Align Business Goals and Banking Services<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your banking services and your business goals must mirror one another for the business to succeed. You also need to have specific guidelines explaining the steps you&#8217;ll need to take to assist you in achieving the identified business goals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In today&#8217;s world, businesses must manage their resources efficiently to help them deal with any challenges that may arise later. Any disconnect between its finances and business strategy will lead to poor implementation and lacklustre budgeting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both of these can cause a business to close down its operations. The only way to learn about the budget&#8217;s impact on operations is to align them. These steps can help you align these two factors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"seeks-insights-from-all-the-company-executives\"><\/span>Seeks Insights from All the Company Executives<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You should include all the executives in the strategy-building process. Ensure they know how financial forecasting can impact strategy building and implementation. While at it, provide them with a demonstration of how their responsibilities can affect its success.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Often, the teams preparing the company expenses aren&#8217;t involved in formulating the strategy. For alignment to occur, both teams must work together to formulate a plan to drive growth.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"prepare-a-long-term-vision-for-the-company\"><\/span>Prepare a Long-term Vision for the Company<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Most budgets only account for twelve months. But, various initiatives may take longer to start performing after their launch. In such a scenario, the twelve-month plan may prove ineffective.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Adopting a long-term approach will allow you to account for such challenges. Ensure you have a long-term plan to complement the annual budget. Use it to find a way to align your banking services and your business.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Strategy is a commonly misused term in banking as a service industry. The only way to execute a strategy is to start by understanding the company.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":821,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[16,25],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/749"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=749"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/749\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":823,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/749\/revisions\/823"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/821"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=749"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=749"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/localhost:8080\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=749"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}